Year for The Data

Source: R/year.R
is_defaar.Rd

Find the year value in column DEFAAR from table tbl_Orgfile when column for year isn't available in the raw data. This is indicated with $Y in column AAR in table tbl_Innlesing.

Usage

is_defaar(id = NULL, con = NULL)

Arguments

con

Connection to database

Value

An integer
